title: 'PITFALL: Declaration via map literals'
pid: d54f341f-024e-4d7d-bf53-d715b7da41c2
body: |2-
  They need a trailing comma,
  and the type signature can be confusing.
  See comments below:

  var m = map [string] Vertex { // type = map string Vertex
    "Bell Labs" : Vertex{
            40.68433, -74.39967,
    },
    "Google" : Vertex{
            37.42202, -122.08408,
    },                          // trailing comma
  }
